<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Assistência Técnica Autorizada | DELLAMED</title>
<script src="https://code.iconify.design/iconify-icon/1.0.7/iconify-icon.min.js"></script>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --navy-1: #002F63;
  --navy-2: #00224A;
  --navy-3: #00122E;
  --navy-darker: #001736;
  --vermelho: #A6192E;
  --vermelho-hover: #8B1526;
  --whatsapp: #25D366;
  --whatsapp-hover: #1da851;
  --amber: #f59e0b;
  --amber-bg: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.10);
  --amber-border: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.30);
  --amber-text: #fde68a;
  --branco: #fff;
  --texto-input: #1e293b;
}
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html, body {
  font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  color: var(--branco);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-1) 0%, var(--navy-2) 50%, var(--navy-3) 100%);
  min-height: 100vh;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-height: 100vh; }
::selection { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.20); color: var(--branco); }
.search-box input::selection { background: rgba(0,47,99,0.20); color: var(--texto-input); }

/* NAV */
nav {
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 50;
  background: rgba(0, 47, 99, 0.50);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
  padding: 16px 24px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
nav img { height: 64px; width: auto; object-fit: contain; }

/* Listra vermelha embaixo do nav, detalhe de marca */
.brand-stripe {
  width: 100%;
  height: 4px;
  background: var(--vermelho);
}

/* MAIN */
main {
  flex-grow: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 1152px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 64px 16px 96px;
}
@media (min-width: 640px) { main { padding-left: 24px; padding-right: 24px; } }
@media (min-width: 1024px) { main { padding-left: 32px; padding-right: 32px; } }

/* HERO */
.hero { text-align: center; max-width: 768px; margin: 0 auto 48px; width: 100%; }
.pill {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 6px 12px;
  border-radius: 9999px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.20);
  box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--branco);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
}
.pill .dot {
  display: inline-flex;
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 9999px;
  background: #4ade80;
  box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(74,222,128,0.60);
}
h1 {
  font-size: 36px;
  line-height: 1.2;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--branco);
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
@media (min-width: 640px) { h1 { font-size: 48px; } }
.hero p {
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: rgba(232, 240, 254, 0.95);
  max-width: 640px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
@media (min-width: 640px) { .hero p { font-size: 22px; } }

/* FILTRO PRODUTO */
.filtro-produto { width: 100%; max-width: 768px; margin: 32px auto 16px; }
.filtro-produto > p {
  font-size: 15px;
  color: rgba(219,234,254,0.90);
  margin: 0 0 10px;
  padding: 0 4px;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.filtro-produto > p strong { color: var(--branco); }
.opcoes { display: flex; gap: 8px; }
.opcoes label { flex: 1; cursor: pointer; }
.opcoes input[type="radio"] {
  position: absolute;
  width: 1px; height: 1px;
  padding: 0; margin: -1px; overflow: hidden;
  clip: rect(0,0,0,0); white-space: nowrap; border: 0;
}
.opcoes .opt {
  padding: 10px 16px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.20);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 500;
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--branco);
  transition: all 0.15s;
}
.opcoes .opt:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.10); }
.opcoes input[type="radio"]:checked + .opt {
  background: var(--branco);
  color: var(--navy-1);
  border-color: var(--branco);
}
#produto-aviso {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: rgba(254, 230, 138, 0.95);
  margin-top: 8px;
  padding: 0 4px;
}

/* SEARCH BOX */
.search-wrap {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 768px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 20;
}
.search-box {
  background: var(--branco);
  padding: 8px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0,0,0,0.10), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 8px;
  transition: box-shadow 0.15s;
}
.search-box:focus-within {
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(255,255,255,0.40);
}
@media (min-width: 640px) { .search-box { flex-direction: row; } }
.input-wrap {
  flex-grow: 1;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0 16px;
}
.input-wrap iconify-icon {
  color: #94a3b8;
  margin-right: 12px;
  font-size: 18px;
}
.search-box input {
  width: 100%;
  background: transparent;
  border: none;
  padding: 14px 0;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 500;
  font-family: inherit;
  color: var(--texto-input); /* preto-azulado: visível no claro do input */
  outline: none;
}
.search-box input::placeholder { color: #94a3b8; font-weight: 400; }
.btn-buscar {
  background: var(--vermelho);
  color: var(--branco);
  padding: 14px 32px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 500;
  font-family: inherit;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.15s, transform 0.05s;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 8px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
}
.btn-buscar:hover:not(:disabled) { background: var(--vermelho-hover); }
.btn-buscar:active:not(:disabled) { transform: scale(0.98); }
.btn-buscar:disabled { opacity: 0.7; cursor: not-allowed; }
.btn-buscar iconify-icon { font-size: 18px; }
#search-hint {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: rgba(219,234,254,0.60);
  margin-top: 8px;
  padding: 0 8px;
}
.hint-erro { color: #fca5a5 !important; }

/* RESULTS */
.results-area {
  width: 100%;
  margin-top: 64px;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.5s;
}
.results-area.show { opacity: 1; }
.results-area.hidden { display: none; }
.results-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 8px;
}
.results-header h2 {
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--branco);
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
}
#results-count {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.70);
}
#results-message {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  background: var(--amber-bg);
  border: 1px solid var(--amber-border);
  border-radius: 16px;
  color: var(--amber-text);
  font-size: 14px;
  align-items: flex-start;
}
#results-message.hidden { display: none; }
#results-message iconify-icon { font-size: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }

.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 24px;
}
@media (min-width: 768px) { .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }

/* CARD */
.card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 24px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: box-shadow 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
}
.card:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.30);
}
.card-bg-icon {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; right: 0;
  padding: 16px;
  opacity: 0.10;
  transform: translateX(16px) translateY(-16px);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.card-bg-icon iconify-icon { font-size: 96px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
.card-top {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: flex-start;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  gap: 12px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
.card-info { min-width: 0; flex: 1; }
.card-info h3 {
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--branco);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
  line-height: 1.3;
}
.card-info .dist {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: rgba(191,219,254,0.70);
  gap: 6px;
}
.card-badges {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: flex-end;
  gap: 6px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 4px;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 500;
  padding: 4px 10px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.badge-horario {
  background: rgba(245,158,11,0.15);
  color: #fde68a;
  border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.30);
}
.badge-mp {
  background: rgba(59,130,246,0.20);
  color: #bfdbfe;
  border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.30);
}

.card-body {
  flex-grow: 1;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
}
.card-body .row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: rgba(219,234,254,0.90);
}
.card-body .row.start { align-items: flex-start; }
.card-body .row.center { align-items: center; }
.card-body iconify-icon {
  color: rgba(147,197,253,0.70);
  font-size: 16px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.card-body .row.start iconify-icon { margin-top: 2px; }

.card-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  margin-top: auto;
}
.btn-action {
  flex: 1;
  padding: 10px 16px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 500;
  font-family: inherit;
  border: 1px solid;
  cursor: pointer;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 8px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.15s;
}
.btn-action iconify-icon { font-size: 18px; }
.btn-wpp {
  background: rgba(37,211,102,0.10);
  border-color: rgba(37,211,102,0.30);
  color: var(--whatsapp);
}
.btn-wpp:hover { background: rgba(37,211,102,0.20); }
.btn-rotas {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
  border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.20);
  color: var(--branco);
}
.btn-rotas:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.20); }

/* Central de pós-vendas (chamada de socorro) */
.central-cta {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 640px;
  margin: 32px auto 0;
  padding: 24px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
  border-radius: 16px;
  text-align: center;
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
}
.central-cta h4 {
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--branco);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.central-cta p {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: rgba(219,234,254,0.85);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.btn-central {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 12px 24px;
  background: var(--whatsapp);
  color: var(--branco);
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.15s;
}
.btn-central:hover { background: var(--whatsapp-hover); }
.btn-central iconify-icon { font-size: 18px; }

/* FOOTER */
footer {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 32px 0;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
  background: var(--navy-darker);
  margin-top: auto;
}
.footer-inner {
  max-width: 1152px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 16px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
}
@media (min-width: 640px) {
  .footer-inner { flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0 24px; }
}
.footer-brand {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  opacity: 0.9;
  color: var(--branco);
}
.footer-brand span {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
}
.footer-copy {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: rgba(191,219,254,0.60);
  font-weight: 500;
}
.footer-social { display: flex; gap: 16px; }
.footer-social a {
  color: rgba(191,219,254,0.60);
  transition: color 0.15s;
  font-size: 20px;
}
.footer-social a:hover { color: var(--branco); }

/* Spinner */
.spin { display: inline-flex; animation: spin 1s linear infinite; }
@keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

/* VER TODAS */
.ver-todas-wrap {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 480px;
  margin: 48px auto 0;
  text-align: center;
}
.btn-ver-todas {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 16px 32px;
  background: var(--vermelho);
  color: var(--branco);
  border: 1px solid var(--vermelho);
  border-radius: 12px;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-family: inherit;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(166, 25, 46, 0.30);
  opacity: 0.92;
}
.btn-ver-todas:hover {
  opacity: 1;
  background: var(--vermelho-hover);
  border-color: var(--vermelho-hover);
  box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(166, 25, 46, 0.40);
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}
.btn-ver-todas:active { transform: translateY(0); }
.btn-ver-todas iconify-icon { font-size: 18px; }
#btn-ver-todas-chevron { transition: transform 0.25s; }
.btn-ver-todas.aberto #btn-ver-todas-chevron { transform: rotate(180deg); }

.todas-area {
  width: 100%;
  margin: 32px -16px 0;
  padding: 40px 16px 48px;
  background: #F4F6FB;
  border-radius: 24px;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.4s;
  color: #1A1F36;
}
@media (min-width: 640px) {
  .todas-area { margin-left: -24px; margin-right: -24px; padding: 48px 24px 56px; }
}
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .todas-area { margin-left: -32px; margin-right: -32px; padding: 56px 32px; }
}
.todas-area.show { opacity: 1; }
.todas-area.hidden { display: none; }
.todas-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 8px;
  max-width: 1152px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  padding: 0 8px;
}
.todas-header h2 {
  font-size: 26px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #002F63;
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  margin: 0;
}
#todas-count {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #6B7280;
  font-weight: 500;
}
#todas-conteudo {
  max-width: 1152px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.uf-bloco {
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}
.uf-titulo {
  font-size: 17px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #002F63;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  padding-bottom: 10px;
  border-bottom: 2px solid #E5E7EB;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
}
.uf-titulo .uf-sigla {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  padding: 4px 9px;
  background: var(--vermelho);
  color: var(--branco);
  border-radius: 4px;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}
.uf-titulo .uf-count {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #6B7280;
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-left: auto;
}
.cards-lista {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 12px;
}
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .cards-lista { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
}
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .cards-lista { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; }
}
.card-mini {
  background: var(--branco);
  border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 16px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 8px;
  transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
}
.card-mini:hover {
  border-color: #C7D2E0;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(20, 60, 150, 0.08);
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}
.card-mini-top {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 10px;
}
.card-mini-nome {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #1A1F36;
  line-height: 1.4;
  flex: 1;
}
.card-mini-local {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: #4A5168;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
}
.card-mini-local iconify-icon {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: #8B92A7;
}
.card-mini-acoes {
  display: flex;
  gap: 6px;
  margin-top: 6px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.btn-mini {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 5px;
  padding: 7px 12px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  border: 1px solid;
  transition: all 0.15s;
  font-family: inherit;
}
.btn-mini iconify-icon { font-size: 13px; }
.btn-mini-wpp {
  background: var(--whatsapp);
  border-color: var(--whatsapp);
  color: var(--branco);
}
.btn-mini-wpp:hover {
  background: var(--whatsapp-hover);
  border-color: var(--whatsapp-hover);
}
.btn-mini-rotas {
  background: var(--branco);
  border-color: #D7DBE5;
  color: #002F63;
}
.btn-mini-rotas:hover {
  background: #F4F6FB;
  border-color: #002F63;
}
.badge-mini-mp {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 3px 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  background: #E6F1FB;
  color: #002F63;
  border: 1px solid #C7DAEC;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Dellamed">
</nav>
<div class="brand-stripe"></div>

<main>

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="pill">
      <span class="dot"></span>
      Rede credenciada em todo o Brasil
    </div>
    <h1>Encontre uma Assistência Técnica Autorizada perto de você!</h1>
    <p>Digite seu CEP para encontrar a autorizada Dellamed mais próxima de você.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="search-wrap">
    <div class="search-box">
      <div class="input-wrap">
        <iconify-icon icon="lucide:map-pin" stroke-width="1.5"></iconify-icon>
        <input type="text" id="search-input" placeholder="Digite seu CEP (ex: 95010-000)" maxlength="9" inputmode="numeric" autocomplete="postal-code">
      </div>
      <button class="btn-buscar" id="search-btn">
        <iconify-icon icon="lucide:search" stroke-width="1.5"></iconify-icon>
        Buscar
      </button>
    </div>
    <p id="search-hint">Buscaremos as autorizadas em até 20 km do seu CEP.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="filtro-produto">
    <p>Seu equipamento é um <strong>monitor de pressão</strong>?</p>
